Image Gallery

#file index.html
1. create a div section and then set a class of gallery
2. include the  image then set the width equal to 200px
3. turn this image into a hyperlink by surrounding it with a pair of <a>

4. we can open this image in a new tap by setting the target attribute to equals _blank
5. then set the href attribute to be the source of th image

6. create a div section with a class of description within div of gallery classs
7. and add some text (just the name of the image) 

8. repeat all of them twice with other images

#file index.html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div>
        <a target="_blank" href="Portofino.jpg">
            <img src="Portofino.jpg" width="200px">
        </a>
        <div class="description">Portofino</div>
    </div>
    <div>
        <a target="_blank" href="lake como.jpg">
            <img src="lake como.jpg" width="200px">
        </a>
        <div class="description">Lake Como</div>
    </div>
    <div>
        <a target="_blank" href="Cinque-Terre.jpg">
            <img src="Cinque-Terre.jpg" width="200px">
        </a>
        <div class="description">Cinque Terre</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>


#file style.css

1. select galllery class and then set css properties


2. select all description class within gallery class and then add some css properties


3. when we hovor over, we’ll change the border color
4. add pseudo-class to gallery class


5. delete the width properties in html file
6. select all img tag within gallery class
7. and then set the img widht to be 100%

8. then we’ll set the width in gallery class to be 200px

9. so basically what we did is that we set the width of each image to be 100% of the width of the gallery ( not 100% of the original image)

#file style.css
.gallery{
    display: inline-block;
    border: 1px solid hsl(0, 1%, 60%);
    margin: 5px;
    width: 200px;
}
.gallery .description{
    padding: 10px;
    text-align: center;
}
.gallery:hover{
    border: 1px solid hsl(240, 1%, 10%);;
}
.gallery img{
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
}
